Dear customers: 
 We wanted to let you know that we'll changing the points redemption system starting January 30th. This means until then you can use the current system to get the rewards you want! 
 After that, we'll be closing down the old system and moving over to a new one. 
 We will suspend the current "PO Points" entrance from 00:00(PST) on January 14th, and close the point redemption system (including Exchange Goods) at 00:00(PST) on January 30th. 
 For users who have submitted points applications, we are actively reviewing them, and the points will arrive as soon as possible. 
 We hope this change makes it easier for you to get what you want out of your experience with us. Thank you for your trust in us, looking forward to serve you better.

Thank you for using and trusting Munbyn print! \nMunbyn print values your privacy and the protection of your personal information. In order to provide you with the functionalities of scanning, printing, hardware connection, and file uploading, we may collect your device information (model), bug monitoring, operation logs (Bluetooth device connection process), and click records for data analysis and feature adaptation. We promise to use the collected information in a lawful, legitimate, specific, and clear manne。 \nIf you have any questions, please feel free to email us at munbynmunbyn@gmail.com, and we will promptly address your concerns.
